                            <comment id="14468799" author="blackdrag" created="Mon, 25 Jan 2010 06:44:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think backporting it would be good, since it reduces the error output, without changing any logic. The resolve calls may cause errors, but they won&apos;t go beyond the CompilationUnit, so there should be no change in logic even if something in the ClassLoader would count requeested classes or such.&lt;/p&gt;
